title: 1964 Cupa României Final
text: The 1964 Cupa României Final was the 26th final of <a href="Romania">Romania</a>'s most prestigious <a href="Association%20football">football</a> cup competition. It was disputed between <a href="FC%20Dinamo%20Bucure%C8%99ti">Dinamo București</a> and <a href="FC%20Steaua%20Bucure%C8%99ti">Steaua București</a>, and was won by <a href="FC%20Dinamo%20Bucure%C8%99ti">Dinamo București</a> after a game with 8 goals. It was the 2nd cup for <a href="FC%20Dinamo%20Bucure%C8%99ti">Dinamo București</a>.
